it','closed','closed','','122-revision-v1','','','2017-08-03 11:39:58','2017-08-03 03:39:58','',122,'http://wss.ruanwenwu.cn/?p=129',0,'revision','',0),(130,1,'2017-08-03 11:43:02','2017-08-03 03:43:02','<strong>CSS3制作动画的几个属性：变形(transform)、转换(transition)和动画(animation)</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>1、animation</strong>\r\n\r\n.box {\r\nwidth: 50px;\r\nheight: 50px;\r\nmargin-left: 100px;\r\nbackground: blue;\r\n/* -webkit-animation-name:\'wobble\';动画属性名，也就是我们前面keyframes定义的动画名\r\n-webkit-animation-duration: 10s;动画持续时间\r\n-webkit-animation-timing-function: ease-in-out; 动画频率，和transition-timing-function是一样的\r\n-webkit-animation-delay: 2s;动画延迟时间\r\n-webkit-animation-iteration-count: 10;定义循环资料，infinite为无限次\r\n-webkit-animation-direction: alternate;定义动画方式 */\r\n-webkit-animation:wobble 10s linear 1s infinite;\r\n}\r\n\r\nkeyframes  :关键帧\r\n@-webkit-keyframes \'wobble\'{\r\n0%{\r\nmargin-top: 50px;\r\nbackground: green;\r\n}\r\n40%{\r\nmargin-top:100px;\r\nbackground: #ccc;\r\n}\r\n60%{\r\nmargin-top:150px;\r\nbackground:red;\r\n}\r\n100%{\r\nmargin-top: 200px;\r\nbackground: pink;\r\n}\r\n}\r\n\r\n<strong>2、transition</strong>\r\n\r\ntransition允许css的属性值在一定的时间区间内平滑地过渡。这种效果可以在鼠标单击、获得焦点、被点击或对元素任何改变中触发。\r\n\r\ntransition主要包含四个属性值：执行变换的属性：transition-property,变换延续的时间：transition-duration,在延续时间段，变换的速率变化transition-timing-function,变换延迟时间transition-delay。\r\n\r\n<span class=\"rule\"><span class=\"attribute\">-webkit-transition</span>:<span class=\"value\"> all .<span class=\"number\">5</span>s ease-in-out <span class=\"number\">1</span>s;</span></span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"rule\"><span class=\"attribute\">-o-transition</span>:<span class=\"value\"> all .<span class=\"number\">5</span>s ease-in-out <span class=\"number\">1</span>s;</span></span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"rule\"><span class=\"attribute\">-moz-transition</span>:<span class=\"value\"> all .<span class=\"number\">5</span>s ease-in-out <span class=\"number\">1</span>s;</span></span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"rule\"><span class=\"attribute\">transition</span>:<span class=\"value\"> all .<span class=\"number\">5</span>s ease-in-out <span class=\"number\">1</span>s;</span></span>\r\n\r\n<strong>3、transform</strong>\r\n\r\ntransform的旋转rotate、扭曲skew、缩放scale和移动translate。\r\n\r\ntransform:rotate(30deg):        transform:translate(100px,20px): transform:scale(2,1.5):    transform:skew(30deg,10deg):    transform-origin:x    y；transform-origin   定位原点\r\n\r\n1、top left | left top 等价于 0 0 | 0% 0%\r\n\r\n2、top | top center | center top 等价于 50% 0\r\n\r\n3、right top | top right 等价于 100% 0\r\n\r\n4、left | left center | center left 等价于 0 50% | 0% 50%\r\n\r\n5、center | center center 等价于 50% 50%（默认值）\r\n\r\n6、right | right center | center right 等价于 100% 50%\r\n\r\n7、bottom left | left bottom 等价于 0 100% | 0% 100%\r\n\r\n8、bottom | bottom center | center bottom 等价于 50% 100%\r\n\r\n9、bottom right | right bottom 等价于 100% 100%\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','css3动画','','inherit','closed','closed','','122-revision-v1','','','2017-08-03 11:43:02','2017-08-03 03:43:02','',122,'http://wss.ruanwenwu.cn/?p=130',0,'revision','',0),(131,1,'2017-08-03 14:57:11','2017-08-03 06:57:11','<strong>CSS3制作动画的几个属性：变形(transform)、转换(transition)和动画(animation)</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>1、animation</strong>\r\n\r\n方式：ease、ease-in、ease-in-out、linear、cubic-bezier\r\n\r\n1、ease：（逐渐变慢）默认值，ease函数等同于贝塞尔曲线(0.25, 0.1, 0.25, 1.0).\r\n\r\n2、linear：（匀速），linear 函数等同于贝塞尔曲线(0.0, 0.0, 1.0, 1.0).\r\n\r\n3、ease-in：(加速)，ease-in 函数等同于贝塞尔曲线(0.42, 0, 1.0, 1.0).\r\n\r\n4、ease-out：（减速），ease-out 函数等同于贝塞尔曲线(0, 0, 0.58, 1.0).\r\n\r\n5、ease-in-out：（加速然后减速），ease-in-out 函数等同于贝塞尔曲线(0.42, 0, 0.58, 1.0)\r\n\r\n6、cubic-bezier：（该值允许你去自定义一个时间曲线）， 特定的cubic-bezier曲线。 (x1, y1, x2, y2)四个值特定于曲线上点P1和点P2。所有值需在[0, 1]区域内，否则无效。\r\n\r\nwidth: 50px;\r\nheight: 50px;\r\nmargin-left: 100px;\r\nbackground: blue;\r\n/* -webkit-animation-name:\'wobble\';动画属性名，也就是我们前面keyframes定义的动画名\r\n-webkit-animation-duration: 10s;动画持续时间\r\n-webkit-animation-timing-function: ease-in-out; 动画频率，和transition-timing-function是一样的\r\n-webkit-animation-delay: 2s;动画延迟时间\r\n-webkit-animation-iteration-count: 10;定义循环资料，infinite为无限次\r\n-webkit-animation-direction: alternate;定义动画方式 */\r\n-webkit-animation:wobble 10s linear 1s infinite;\r\n}\r\n\r\nkeyframes  :关键帧\r\n@-webkit-keyframes \'wobble\'{\r\n0%{\r\nmargin-top: 50px;\r\nbackground: green;\r\n}\r\n40%{\r\nmargin-top:100px;\r\nbackground: #ccc;\r\n}\r\n60%{\r\nmargin-top:150px;\r\nbackground:red;\r\n}\r\n100%{\r\nmargin-top: 200px;\r\nbackground: pink;\r\n}\r\n}\r\n\r\n<strong>2、transition</strong>\r\n\r\ntransition允许css的属性值在一定的时间区间内平滑地过渡。这种效果可以在鼠标单击、获得焦点、被点击或对元素任何改变中触发。\r\n\r\ntransition主要包含四个属性值：执行变换的属性：transition-property,变换延续的时间：transition-duration,在延续时间段，变换的速率变化transition-timing-function,变换延迟时间transition-delay。\r\n\r\n<span class=\"rule\"><span class=\"attribute\">-webkit-transition</span>:<span class=\"value\"> all .<span class=\"number\">5</span>s ease-in-out <span class=\"number\">1</span>s;</span></span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"rule\"><span class=\"attribute\">-o-transition</span>:<span class=\"value\"> all .<span class=\"number\">5</span>s ease-in-out <span class=\"number\">1</span>s;</span></span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"rule\"><span class=\"attribute\">-moz-transition</span>:<span class=\"value\"> all .<span class=\"number\">5</span>s ease-in-out <span class=\"number\">1</span>s;</span></span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"rule\"><span class=\"attribute\">transition</span>:<span class=\"value\"> all .<span class=\"number\">5</span>s ease-in-out <span class=\"number\">1</span>s;</span></span>\r\n\r\n<strong>3、transform</strong>\r\n\r\ntransform的旋转rotate、扭曲skew、缩放scale和移动translate。\r\n\r\ntransform:rotate(30deg):        transform:translate(100px,20px): transform:scale(2,1.5):    transform:skew(30deg,10deg):    transform-origin:x    y；transform-origin   定位原点\r\n\r\n1、top left | left top 等价于 0 0 | 0% 0%\r\n\r\n2、top | top center | center top 等价于 50% 0\r\n\r\n3、right top | top right 等价于 100% 0\r\n\r\n4、left | left center | center left 等价于 0 50% | 0% 50%\r\n\r\n5、center | center center 等价于 50% 50%（默认值）\r\n\r\n6、right | right center | center right 等价于 100% 50%\r\n\r\n7、bottom left | left bottom 等价于 0 100% | 0% 100%\r\n\r\n8、bottom | bottom center | center bottom 等价于 50% 100%\r\n\r\n9、bottom right | right bottom 等价于 100% 100%\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','css3动画','','inherit','closed','closed','','122-revision-v1','','','2017-08-03 14:57:11','2017-08-03 06:57:11','',122,'http://wss.ruanwenwu.cn/?p=131',0,'revision','',0),(133,1,'2017-08-16 18:50:35','2017-08-16 10:50:35','1、超出显示点点\r\n\r\noverflow:hidden;\r\nwhite-space: nowrap;\r\ntext-overflow:ellipsis;\r\n\r\nclip : 　不显示省略标记（...），而是简单的裁切\r\n<strong>ellipsis</strong> : 　当对象内文本溢出时显示省略标记（...）\r\n\r\n2、body撑不开\r\n\r\nbody和html高度给100%\r\n\r\n3、text-align:justify;段落文字两端对齐','css知识点','','publish','open','open','','css%e7%9f%a5%e8%af%86%e7%82%b9','','','2017-08-29 16:08:14','2017-08-29 08:08:14','',0,'http://wss.ruanwenwu.cn/?p=133',0,'post','',0),(134,1,'2017-08-16 18:50:35','2017-08-16 10:50:35','1、超出显示点点\r\n\r\noverflow:hidden;\r\nwhite-space: nowrap;\r\ntext-overflow:ellipsis;\r\n\r\nclip : 　不显示省略标记（...），而是简单的裁切\r\n<strong>ellipsis</strong> : 　当对象内文本溢出时显示省略标记（...）\r\n\r\n2、body撑不开\r\n\r\nbody和html高度给100%\r\n\r\n3、','css知识点','','inherit','closed','closed','','133-revision-v1','','','2017-08-16 18:50:35','2017-08-16 10:50:35','',133,'http://wss.ruanwenwu.cn/?p=134',0,'revision','',0),(135,1,'2017-08-16 18:52:19','2017-08-16 10:52:19','&lt;script&gt;\r\nif (/Android (\\d+\\.\\d+)/.test(navigator.userAgent)) {\r\nif (parseFloat(RegExp.$1) &gt; 2.3) {\r\nvar phoneScale = parseInt(window.screen.width) / 750;\r\ndocument.write(\'&lt;meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=750, minimum-scale=\' + phoneScale + \', maximum-scale=\' + phoneScale + \', target-densitydpi=device-dpi\" /&gt;\');\r\n} else {\r\ndocument.write(\'&lt;meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=750, target-densitydpi=device-dpi\" /&gt;\');\r\n}\r\n} else {\r\ndocument.write(\'&lt;meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=750,user-scalable=no, target-densitydpi=device-dpi\" /&gt;\');\r\n}\r\n&lt;/script&gt;','js移动端适配','','publish','open','open','','js%e7%a7%bb%e5%8a%a8%e7%ab%af%e9%80%82%e9%85%8d','','','2017-08-16 18:52:19','2017-08-16 10:52:19','',0,'http://wss.ruanwenwu.cn/?p=135',0,'post','',0),(136,1,'2017-08-16 18:52:19','2017-08-16 10:52:19','&lt;script&gt;\r\nif (/Android (\\d+\\.\\d+)/.test(navigator.userAgent)) {\r\nif (parseFloat(RegExp.$1) &gt; 2.3) {\r\nvar phoneScale = parseInt(window.screen.width) / 750;\r\ndocument.write(\'&lt;meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=750, minimum-scale=\' + phoneScale + \', maximum-scale=\' + phoneScale + \', target-densitydpi=device-dpi\" /&gt;\');\r\n} else {\r\ndocument.write(\'&lt;meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=750, target-densitydpi=device-dpi\" /&gt;\');\r\n}\r\n} else {\r\ndocument.write(\'&lt;meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=750,user-scalable=no, target-densitydpi=device-dpi\" /&gt;\');\r\n}\r\n&lt;/script&gt;','js移动端适配','','inherit','closed','closed','','135-revision-v1','','','2017-08-16 18:52:19','2017-08-16 10:52:19','',135,'http://wss.ruanwenwu.cn/?p=136',0,'revision','',0),(137,1,'2017-08-17 14:00:57','2017-08-17 06:00:57','1、ng-app=\" \"  定义angularJS的使用范围；\r\n\r\n2、ng-init=\"变量=值;变量=\'值\'\"  初始化变量的值，有多个变量时，中间用分号隔开；\r\n\r\n3、ng-model=\"变量\"  定义变量名；\r\n\r\n4、ng-bind=\"变量\"  绑定变量名，获取该变量的数据。这里的变量就是第3条的变量名。但是一般都用双重花括号来获取变量的值，比如：{{变量}}。','初始AngularJS','','publish','open','open','','%e5%88%9d%e5%a7%8bangularjs','','','2017-08-17 14:00:57','2017-08-17 06:00:57','',0,'http://wss.ruanwenwu.cn/?p=137',0,'post','',0),(138,1,'2017-08-17 14:00:57','2017-08-17 06:00:57','1、ng-app=\" \"  定义angularJS的使用范围；\r\n\r\n2、ng-init=\"变量=值;变量=\'值\'\"  初始化变量的值，有多个变量时，中间用分号隔开；\r\n\r\n3、ng-model=\"变量\"  定义变量名；\r\n\r\n4、ng-bind=\"变量\"  绑定变量名，获取该变量的数据。这里的变量就是第3条的变量名。但是一般都用双重花括号来获取变量的值，比如：{{变量}}。','初始AngularJS','','inherit','closed','closed','','137-revision-v1','','','2017-08-17 14:00:57','2017-08-17 06:00:57','',137,'http://wss.ruanwenwu.cn/?p=138',0,'revision','',0),(139,1,'2017-08-22 09:23:51','2017-08-22 01:23:51','1、AngularJS 表达式写在双大括号内：{{ expression }}，与ng-bind指令有异曲同工之妙用。\r\n\r\n2、表达式书写的位置“输出”数据。\r\n\r\n3、表达式包含文字、运算符和变量  ，数字，字符串，对象，数组。\r\n\r\n4、AngularJS 表达式 与 JavaScript 表达式\r\n\r\n类似于 JavaScript 表达式，AngularJS 表达式可以包含字母，操作符，变量。\r\n\r\n与 JavaScript 表达式不同，AngularJS 表达式可以写在 HTML 中。\r\n\r\n与 JavaScript 表达式不同，AngularJS 表达式不支持条件判断，循环及异常。\r\n\r\n与 JavaScript 表达式不同，AngularJS 表达式支持过滤器。','AngularJS 表达式','','publish','open','open','','angularjs-%e8%a1%a8%e8%be%be%e5%bc%8f','','','2017-08-22 11:09:48','2017-08-22 03:09:48','',0,'http://wss.ruanwenwu.cn/?p=139',0,'post','',0),(140,1,'2017-08-22 09:23:51','2017-08-22 01:23:51','AngularJS 表达式写在双大括号内：<strong>{{ expression }}</strong>。','AngularJS 表达式','','inherit','closed','closed','','139-revision-v1','','','2017-08-22 09:23:51','2017-08-22 01:23:51','',139,'http://wss.ruanwenwu.cn/?p=140',0,'revision','',0),(141,1,'2017-08-22 10:42:26','2017-08-22 02:42:26','1、AngularJS 表达式写在双大括号内：{{ expression }}，与ng-bind指令有异曲同工之妙用。\n\n2、表达式书写的位置“输出”数据。\n\n3、表达式包含文字、运算符和变量  ，数字，字符串，对象，数组。','AngularJS 表达式','','inherit','closed','closed','','139-autosave-v1','','','2017-08-22 10:42:26','2017-08-22 02:42:26','',139,'http://wss.ruanwenwu.cn/?p=141',0,'revision','',0),(142,1,'2017-08-22 10:21:18','2017-08-22 02:21:18','1、AngularJS 表达式写在双大括号内：{{ expression }}，与ng-bind指令有异曲同工之妙用。\r\n\r\n2、表达式书写的位置“输出”数据。\r\n\r\n3、表达式包含文字、运算符和变量。','AngularJS 表达式','','inherit','closed','closed','','139-revision-v1','','','2017-08-22 10:21:18','2017-08-22 02:21:18','',139,'http://wss.ruanwenwu.cn/?p=142',0,'revision','',0),(143,1,'2017-08-22 10:42:28','2017-08-22 02:42:28','1、AngularJS 表达式写在双大括号内：{{ expression }}，与ng-bind指令有异曲同工之妙用。\r\n\r\n2、表达式书写的位置“输出”数据。\r\n\r\n3、表达式包含文字、运算符和变量  ，数字，字符串，对象，数组。','AngularJS 表达式','','inherit','closed','closed','','139-revision-v1','','','2017-08-22 10:42:28','2017-08-22 02:42:28','',139,'http://wss.ruanwenwu.cn/?p=143',0,'revision','',0),(144,1,'2017-08-22 11:04:25','2017-08-2